{
  "stem": "9908.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we didn't realize it's just around the corner of us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember one Shabbos, everybody was out and having a good time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They say Hitler is going to invade Czechoslovakia, because he wants Sudetenland from Czechoslovakia, which belonged once to Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He wanted this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He gave them an ultimatum.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Czechs didn't have no choice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They gave him back Sudetenland.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Six months later, he said to Poland, he wants Zaolzie.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This was a-- a town near to the German border.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He wants Zaolzie.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The Poles said they will not give him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But for some reason, six months later, they gave back to Hitler Zaolzie.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "As he gave him back, he said, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That means, I have no-- saying that I want more land.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That's what I wanted, Sudetenland and Zaolzie.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Six months later, the war broke out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "A lot of politicians talked about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I remember my father used to be also the head of the union-- of tailors' union-- in Ozorkow.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they used to have meetings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When they come for the meetings, they been discussing politics, too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a lot of Yiddens said, see?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hitler will attack Poland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- but the Poles were too stupid to realize.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because just before, maybe six months before the war, there was in the-- in the senate, there was a lady named [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She gave a project into the senate that the Yidden are not supposed to cut their cows.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They're supposed to shoot them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's un-humane.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's un-humane to-- to cut the-- the throat from the-- from the cows.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And this was going on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That we start feeling the anti-Semitism in Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was going on for months and months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "By the time Hitler-- they were thinking about the Jews-- 'cause they couldn't-- about their meat.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
